# üß© ServBox ‚Äî Hardware Parts Description

This document details each hardware component used in the ServBox mini-ITX Proxmox homelab server, including its purpose, compatibility notes, and reasons for selection.

---

## üß† CPU ‚Äî AMD Ryzen 7 5700G
**Cores:** 8  
**Threads:** 16  
**Base Clock:** 3.8 GHz  
**Boost Clock:** 4.6 GHz  
**Graphics:** Integrated Radeon Vega (useful before GPU installation)

### Why it was chosen
- Strong multi-core performance for virtualization  
- Integrated GPU allows headless setup without a dedicated GPU  
- Low power usage for a home server  
- AM4 platform compatibility with ITX motherboards  

---

## üßµ RAM ‚Äî 32GB DDR4 (2√ó16GB)
**Speed:** 3000‚Äì3200 MHz  
**Type:** DDR4  
**Future Upgrades:** Expandable to 64GB

### Why it was chosen
- 32GB allows running 6‚Äì10 VMs comfortably  
- Dual-channel improves overall VM performance  
- Affordable and upgradeable later  

---

## üß© Motherboard ‚Äî ASRock B550M-ITX/AC
**Form Factor:** Mini-ITX  
**Chipset:** AMD B550  
**Features:**
- Integrated Wi-Fi & Bluetooth  
- NVMe M.2 slot  
- PCIe for dedicated GPU  
- BIOS supports Ryzen 5000 series  

### Why it was chosen
- Supports Ryzen 5700G out of the box  
- ITX size fits the NR200P case  
- Strong BIOS and virtualization support  

---

## üßä CPU Cooler ‚Äî ID-COOLING IS-67-XT
**Height:** 67mm (low profile)  
**Heatpipes:** 6  
**Fan:** 120mm slim (15mm thick)  

### Why it was chosen
- Fits perfectly inside the NR200P V2  
- Low noise & great thermals for SFF  
- Reliable cooling for 8-core CPU  

---

## üîå Power Supply ‚Äî Cooler Master V850 SFX Gold
**Wattage:** 850W  
**Certification:** 80+ Gold  
**Size:** SFX (Small Form Factor)

### Why it was chosen
- Needed for NR200P ITX case  
- Plenty of overhead for future GPU upgrades  
- High efficiency + quiet operation  

---

## üì¶ Case ‚Äî Cooler Master NR200P V2
**Form Factor:** Mini-ITX  
**Features:**
- Tempered glass or mesh panel  
- Supports large GPUs  
- Great airflow for SFF  
- Clean cable routing options  

### Why it was chosen
- Widely considered the best small-form-factor case  
- Excellent airflow for multi-VM workloads  
- Minimalist aesthetic  

---

## üéÆ GPU ‚Äî Nvidia GTX 1070 (optional for later)
**Compute Uses:**
- GPU passthrough  
- Hashcat  
- Machine learning (PyTorch/CUDA)  
- Computer vision workloads  

### Why it will be added later
- Gives the server GPU-accelerated compute power  
