---

## ‚ö° Storage ‚Äî 2TB NVMe SSD
**Type:** NVMe M.2  
**Capacity:** 2TB  
**Future expansion:** Additional SATA SSDs or external storage

### Why it was chosen
- Fast VM disk performance  
- Lower power usage  
- Enough room for many OS images and snapshots  

---

## üìù Summary
This hardware configuration is optimized to:
- run Proxmox efficiently  
- support multiple VMs for labs  
- fit into a compact form factor  
- grow into a more powerful environment over time

As upgrades are made, this file will be updated to reflect changes in the system.




